DATA DISCLAIMER

This software was developed and tested using data from a proprietary
longitudinal cohort of oldest old patients with MCI, collected under
an approved ethics protocol. The clinical data are not distributed
with this repository and cannot be shared due to patient privacy and
ethical constraints.

The synthetic example dataset included in the data/ folder is provided
solely for the purpose of demonstrating the software pipeline and does
not correspond to real patient data.
